=============================== PYTHON NOTES ================================

-----------------------
1. Expected Data Types 
- Integer : Use"d"     
- String  : Use"s"
- Float   : Use"f"
-----------------------

---------------------------------------
2. How many Characters to fit
- Enter the code as "... :45(datatype)"
---------------------------------------

----------------------------------------------------------
3. Alignment of Data
- "<" (Align to the left of (Characters to fit) numbers)
- ">" (Align to the right of (Characters to fit) numbers)
- "^" (Align to the center of (Characters to fit) numbers)
----------------------------------------------------------

----------------------------------------------------------------------------
4. Character to pad the Additional spaces
- "(Input)":(Character to pad)(Alignment Symbol)(Number)(Selected Data Type)
----------------------------------------------------------------------------

------------------------------------------
5. Set Decimal Points for Float Data Types
- '(Number):.(Number of Decimal Points)f'
------------------------------------------

-----------------------------------------------------------------------
6. Ask user to Input
- (variable Name) = (Expected Data type)(input('(Question/Statement)'))
-----------------------------------------------------------------------


